        },
        {
            "text": "The systematic uncertainties related to the detector description, signal-extraction procedure and Monte Carlo statistics are assumed to be uncorrelated between the LEP experiments. ",
            "section": "Average LEP fragmentation fractions",
            "paragraph_rank": 19,
            "section_rank": 6
        },
        {
            "text": "The uncertainties related to the modelling of Z \u2192 cc and Z \u2192 bb events are taken as the correlated uncertainties. ",
